近年來加拿大的幾個城市的海狸種群數量有所回升。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Canada's beaver problem|url=https://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/canadas-beaver-problem/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Campbell|date=2017-07-05|first=Meagan|work=Maclean's|publisher=Rogers Digital Media|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805060400/https://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/canadas-beaver-problem/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title='He's quite shy': Beaver sightings on the rise in Calgary|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/2747760/hes-quite-shy-beaver-sightings-on-the-rise-in-calgary/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Smith|date=2016-06-07|first=Kim|work=Global News|publisher=Corus Entertainment Inc.|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805055558/https://globalnews.ca/news/2747760/hes-quite-shy-beaver-sightings-on-the-rise-in-calgary/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Torbe">{{Cite web|title=Leave it to beavers, they're loving the big-city life|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/leave-it-to-beavers-theyre-loving-the-big-city-life/article4145097/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Mittelstaedt|date=2001-03-05|first=Martin|work=The Globe and Mail|publisher=The Woodbridge Company|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806022348/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/leave-it-to-beavers-theyre-loving-the-big-city-life/article4145097/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[卡爾加里|卡爾加里]]的河狸數量在2016年約200隻， 大部分棲息在[[弓河|弓河]]及[[埃爾博河|埃爾博河]]附近。<ref name="canurnu">{{Cite web|title=Vancouver's urban-beaver plan focuses on enhancing habitats|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/vancouvers-urban-beaver-plan-focuses-on-enhancing-habitats/article28530523/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=McCutcheon|date=2016-02-02|first=Andrew|work=The Globe and Mail|publisher=The Woodbridge Company|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805075247/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/vancouvers-urban-beaver-plan-focuses-on-enhancing-habitats/article28530523/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但這些河狸會對公園附近的樹木造成一定程度的破壞，若河狸的破壞造成不必要的損失，防治措施就變得有必要。市政府會使用多種方法來防治海狸預防損害，例如在樹幹周圍放置網狀鐵絲網，在海岸線附近種植對海狸不會去啃食的樹木，在大壩下設置排水系統以控制水位；並放置使河狸即死的陷阱使河狸敬而遠之，艾伯塔環境部門不允許將捕抓的河狸重定位治其他區域。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Beavers|url=https://www.calgary.ca/CSPS/Parks/Pages/Planning-and-Operations/Pest-Management/Beavers.aspx|accessdate=2019-07-29|year=2018|publisher=City of Calgary|archive-date=2020-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424232925/https://www.calgary.ca/CSPS/Parks/Pages/Planning-and-Operations/Pest-Management/Beavers.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

美洲河狸有時會漫遊到下[[渥太華|渥太華]]一些區域，如[[國會山莊_(加拿大)|國會山莊]]、[[少校山公園|少校山公園]]、和[[火花街道_(渥太華)|火花街道]]<ref name="Ottbe">{{Cite web|title=Carry on, wayward beaver: Our national animal visits Major's Hill Park|url=https://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/carry-on-wayward-beaver-our-national-animal-visits-majors-hill-park|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Douglas|date=2019-05-25|first=Kayla|work=Ottawa Citizen|publisher=Postmedia Network Inc|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805074231/https://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/carry-on-wayward-beaver-our-national-animal-visits-majors-hill-park|dead-url=no}}</ref>在都會區抓到的河狸通常會送到野生動物中心，隨後在離[[綠帶城_(渥太華)|綠帶城]]近的[[渥太華河|渥太華河]]附近野放。 2011年，渥太華開始捕抓河狸，將其棲息在[[斯提威爾|斯提威爾]][[調水池|調水池]]的河狸，及位於在渥太華[[加蒂諾公園|加蒂諾公園]]（Gatineau Park）南部入口以南4公里處的河狸移除。<ref name="Gatin">{{Cite web|title=NCC keeping a close eye on Gatineau Park's beaver population|url=https://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/ncc-keeping-a-close-eye-on-gatineau-parks-beaver-population|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Butler|date=2014-05-20|first=Don|work=Ottawa Citizen|publisher=Postmedia Network Inc|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805080448/https://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/ncc-keeping-a-close-eye-on-gatineau-parks-beaver-population|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=City of Ottawa joins fight against the beaver|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/canada/city-of-ottawa-joins-fight-against-the-beaver|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=McMahon|date=2011-11-02|first=Tamsin|work=The National Post|publisher=Postmedia Network Inc.}}</ref>該公園位於渥太華河的[[魁北克|魁北克]]一側，是北美最密集的河狸種群之一，2011年對該公園的空中盤查顯示有272個河狸群落，裡頭有1,100多隻海狸。[[國家首都委員會|國家首都委員會]]（National Capital Commission）對加蒂諾公園的美洲河狸種群進行監控，以保護當地基礎設施並維護公共安全。
[[File:Cause_no_one_wanted_to_believe_me_(2876676107).jpg|缩略图]]游泳的河狸]]
[[多倫多市政府|多倫多市政府]]和[[多倫多及地區保護局|多倫多及地區保護局]]（TRCA）並未追踪棲息在多倫多的河狸種群數量，<ref name="canurnu">{{Cite web|title=Vancouver's urban-beaver plan focuses on enhancing habitats|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/vancouvers-urban-beaver-plan-focuses-on-enhancing-habitats/article28530523/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=McCutcheon|date=2016-02-02|first=Andrew|work=The Globe and Mail|publisher=The Woodbridge Company}}</ref>儘管在2001年有統計出有數百隻河狸棲息在該地。<ref name="Torbe">{{Cite web|title=Leave it to beavers, they're loving the big-city life|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/leave-it-to-beavers-theyre-loving-the-big-city-life/article4145097/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Mittelstaedt|date=2001-03-05|first=Martin|work=The Globe and Mail|publisher=The Woodbridge Company}}</ref>海狸通常在安大略湖的海岸線上發現，並貫穿整個城市的水路通道，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Featured Mammal: Beaver (Castor canadensis)|url=https://www.toronto.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9718-Biodiversity-MammalsBook-Division-Planning-And-Development-part1.pdf|accessdate=2019-07-29|date=January 2011|work=Mammals of Toronto: A Guide to a remarkable world|publisher=City of Toronto|archive-date=2020-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200601204819/https://www.toronto.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9718-Biodiversity-MammalsBook-Division-Planning-And-Development-part1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>尤其在[[唐河_(安大略)|唐河]]、[[含伯河|含伯河]]及[[紅河_(加拿大)|紅河]]常出現；跟多倫多水道相鄰的溝壑系統，及[[多倫多群島|多倫多群島]]。多倫多市政府沒有任何計劃來控制都市的河狸種群，然而都市林業部門有時會在一些樹木的樹幹周圍安裝的鐵絲網圍欄，以防止它們被海狸啃壞。<ref name="mesh">{{Cite web|title=Trees in parks & ravines - beavers|url=https://www.toronto.ca/311/knowledgebase/kb/docs/articles/parks,-forestry-and-recreation/urban-forestry/trees-in-parks-and-ravines-beavers.html|accessdate=2019-07-29|year=2018|work=311 Toronto|publisher=City of Toronto}}</ref>2013年，在紅河沿岸安裝了流量矯直機，以防止河狸水壩淹沒河流。在安裝前，河狸建造的水壩導致部分河道被洪水淹沒。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Beaver Baffler, invasive species grant help out Rouge Valley watershed|url=https://www.toronto.com/news-story/4262106-beaver-baffler-invasive-species-grant-help-out-rouge-valley-watershed/|accessdate=2019-08-14|author=Adler|date=2013-12-09|first=Mike|work=toronto.com|publisher=Metroland Media Group|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805085241/https://www.toronto.com/news-story/4262106-beaver-baffler-invasive-species-grant-help-out-rouge-valley-watershed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2017年份的報告中，大多倫多地區動物群引起的事件，河狸的分數為L4。該分數是針對那些在大多倫多地區農村地區種群數量固定來算，但在大多倫多地區都會區種群數量仍可能容易遭受其棲息地長期衰退的物種評分影響而重新評分。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Annual Local Occurrence Score and Local Rank Update: Terrestrial Fauna and Flora Species, and Vegetation Communities|url=https://trca.ca/app/uploads/2017/07/Local-occurrence-update_2016.pdf|accessdate=2019-07-29|date=July 2017|publisher=Toronto and Region Conservation Authority|archive-date=2019-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729202534/https://trca.ca/app/uploads/2017/07/Local-occurrence-update_2016.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最近河狸的種群有往外擴散到其他都市的趨勢， [[傑里科海灘|傑里科海灘]]在2000年初就有河狸定居，2008年起開始出現在溫哥華其他區域。數個組群的河狸在2016年定居溫哥華少數區域，<ref name="canurnu">{{Cite web|title=Vancouver's urban-beaver plan focuses on enhancing habitats|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/vancouvers-urban-beaver-plan-focuses-on-enhancing-habitats/article28530523/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=McCutcheon|date=2016-02-02|first=Andrew|work=The Globe and Mail|publisher=The Woodbridge Company}}</ref><ref name="Vanbe">{{Cite web|title=Leave it to beavers: Toothy rodents fell dozens of trees in Vancouver|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/2432724/leave-it-to-beavers-toothy-rodents-fell-dozens-of-trees-in-vancouver/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Judd|date=2016-01-04|first=Amy|work=Global News|publisher=Corus Entertainment Inc.|archive-date=2020-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615001054/https://globalnews.ca/news/2432724/leave-it-to-beavers-toothy-rodents-fell-dozens-of-trees-in-vancouver/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中較注目[[斯坦利公園生態協會|斯坦利公園生態協會]]（Stanley Park Ecology Society）觀察到有5隻河狸在其管理的[[河狸湖|河狸湖]]定居，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Stanley Park wildlife|url=https://vancouver.ca/parks-recreation-culture/wildlife-.aspx|accessdate=2019-07-29|year=2019|publisher=City of Vancouver|archive-date=2020-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416202405/https://vancouver.ca/parks-recreation-culture/wildlife-.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年並觀察到有一對河狸在[[希集公園|希集公園]] （Hinge Park）建水壩。 [[溫哥華公園及康樂局|溫哥華公園及康樂局]] （Vancouver Board of Parks and Recreation）批准了一項河狸復育計畫，將在2016年促使[[奧運村|奧運村]]附近河狸數量增長。

2019年[[温尼伯|溫尼伯]]大約有100隻河狸沿著城市的河流和小溪生活。<ref name="Winbea">{{Cite web|title=Winnipeg man stunned after beaver shot and killed outside his home|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/5330745/winnipeg-man-stunned-after-beaver-shot-and-killed-outside-his-home/|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Scarpelli|date=2019-05-30|first=Joe|work=Global News|publisher=Corus Entertainment Inc.|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729013420/https://globalnews.ca/news/5330745/winnipeg-man-stunned-after-beaver-shot-and-killed-outside-his-home/|dead-url=no}}</ref>溫尼伯市在2012年收到與河狸有關的損害的投訴後，於同年冬天沿阿西尼博因河沿岸的樹幹周圍放置了鐵絲網，以及用來殺河狸的陷阱。跟艾伯塔省同樣不允許對海狸進行實時捕獲和遷移。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Winnipeg should stop killing problem beavers, St. James resident says|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/winnipeg-beavers-kill-traps-1.4696409|accessdate=2019-07-29|author=Glowacki|date=2018-07-08|first=Laura|work=CBC News|publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|archive-date=2018-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819122032/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manitoba/winnipeg-beavers-kill-traps-1.4696409|dead-url=no}}</ref>溫尼伯市區每年僱用一名承包商，一年換10次人來管理溫尼伯的海狸族群，根據[[曼尼托巴省|曼尼托巴省]]的《野生動植物法》，溫尼伯有權使用槍支處置河狸。

==== 美國 ====
[[File:Lincoln_Park_North_Pond_Beaver_Lodge_Dec_4,_2009.jpg|左]]的河狸巢穴]]
幾個美國城市近年來不時目擊出現河狸，代表美國長年保育結果及河流環境改善使得河狸回歸，重新引入也將河狸安置在其都會區範圍內，這些區域原已長達百年再沒出沒過河狸，現在在這些區域回歸再出現，不僅如此，甚至在不曾出現的區域也發現有河狸族群棲息。 在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]，一些河狸返回該城市並在[[林肯公园_(芝加哥)|林肯公園]]北的池塘附近建立家園，1994起便有記錄重新定居該公園北池塘的河狸，但[[芝加哥公園|芝加哥公園區]]和林肯公園保護區的人員將河狸視為害獸，後者人員擔心該區域的樹木遭到該地河狸啃壞。 2009年3月，他們雇用負責移除河狸的驅逐員，用活套誘捕器移除一個河狸家庭，但卻意外使該家庭的母河狸陷入網羅並溺水身亡。每隻河狸個隻的搬遷費為4,000至4,500美元。[[伊利諾伊州自然資源部|伊利諾伊州自然資源部]]（Illinois Department of Natural Resources）野生生物學家史考特‧加羅（Scott Garrow）認為，遷移河狸是“浪費時間”。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Tales from an Urban Wilderness: Wildlife's Struggle for Survival in a Park Where City & Wilderness Meet|url=https://archive.org/details/talesfromurbanwi0000holi|last=Holingue, Scott|publisher=Chicago Historical Bookworks|location=Chicago, IL|date=1994|page=[https://archive.org/details/talesfromurbanwi0000holi/page/140 140]|isbn=978-0-924772-25-2}}</ref><ref name="myfoxchicago.com">{{Cite news|title=Park District Kills Beaver in Lincoln Park|date=April 2009|work=MyFoxChicago|url=http://www.myfoxchicago.com/dpp/news/beaver_north_pond_apr09|accessdate=2009-12-04|archive-date=2010-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100529063950/http://www.myfoxchicago.com/dpp/news/beaver_north_pond_apr09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Why are there signs that claim the Park District murdered a beaver?|author=Greenfield, John|url=http://chicago.timeout.com/articles/museums-culture/74267/why-are-there-signs-that-claim-the-park-district-murdered-a-beaver|work=Time Out Chicago|date=May 7–13, 2009|accessdate=2009-12-04|archive-date=2009-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090522035451/http://chicago.timeout.com/articles/museums-culture/74267/why-are-there-signs-that-claim-the-park-district-murdered-a-beaver|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Inside">{{Cite news|author=Boehm, Kiersten|title=Lincoln Park Beaver Relocated|work=Inside at Your News Chicago, IL Edition|date=2008-11-14|url=http://www.insideonline.com/|accessdate=2009-12-04|archive-date=2009-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091213145734/http://www.insideonline.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[马丁内斯_(加利福尼亚州)|馬丁內斯]]市中心，2006年有一對河狸在[[阿罕布拉溪|阿罕布拉溪]]定居。隨後在該地定居的河狸建造了約30英尺寬、6英尺高的水壩，該地一半的柳樹被經過的河狸啃掉，都被用去建水壩，當地的河狸族群將阿罕布拉溪的某個絹流變成了多個河狸適居的地盤，建了多個水壩和池子。作為其1999年970萬美元的洪水改善項目的一部分。 當市議會由於擔心洪水而要移除河狸時，當地居民組織起來保護當地的河狸，成立了一個名為“值得水壩”的組織。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Moment of truth for Martinez beavers|url=http://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Moment-of-truth-for-Martinez-beavers-3287204.php|author=Jones, Carolyn|date=2008-04-16|work=San Francisco Chronicle|accessdate=2020-06-09|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609142548/https://www.sfgate.com/bayarea/article/Moment-of-truth-for-Martinez-beavers-3287204.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Beavers, water, & the learning curve|url=http://www.martinezbeavers.org|work=martinezbeavers.org|accessdate=2020-09-16|archive-date=2018-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824172457/http://www.martinezbeavers.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>解決方案有安裝流量矯直機通過河狸水壩，這樣池子的水位就能維持平衡。
